product.name: iPhone 16® Clear MagSafe® Compatible Phone Case
product.description:
• Keep it sleek with a clear Phone Case. Easily power up your iPhone thanks to the MagSafe Compatibility!
  • Fits iPhone 16®
  • Protects your device from scratches, dust and debris. This will not protect your device from traumatic events such as being dropped.
  • Warning: This product can expose you to chemicals including Bisphenol A (BPA), which is known to the State of California to cause birth defects or other reproductive harm. For more information, go to www. P65Warnings.ca.gov/product
  • Country of Origin: Imported
